reviewText: Cool movies, great addition to my movies collection.

The picture quality was very poor, even for having been originally filmed in the 1970s. Also, I did not care much for the content. All the movies came across as extremely low budget films, and not in good taste. I put my copy into my DVD Grinder/Shedder. There's no need to keep something I do not intend on watching again.
